1
00:00:18,980 --> 00:00:24,420
♪It's a sordid story that you've made♪

2
00:00:26,700 --> 00:00:32,700
♪Up to fill my mind with doubts and pain♪

3
00:00:34,780 --> 00:00:40,220
♪Blood I shed, and tears I wept,
are you satisfied?♪

4
00:00:40,220 --> 00:00:42,540
♪Enjoying what's mine♪

5
00:00:42,540 --> 00:00:49,500
♪Have you found a way
to bury guilt and shame♪

6
00:00:50,540 --> 00:00:55,020
♪I'm coming back to life♪

7
00:00:55,020 --> 00:00:58,700
♪Through the seven gates of death♪

8
00:00:58,700 --> 00:01:02,820
♪I'm coming back survived♪

9
00:01:02,820 --> 00:01:06,580
♪Feeling great to see you fall♪

10
00:01:06,580 --> 00:01:10,820
♪I'm taking back what's mine♪

11
00:01:10,820 --> 00:01:15,340
♪Bringing horror to the battlefield♪

12
00:01:15,340 --> 00:01:19,060
♪Lay it to waste♪

13
00:01:19,060 --> 00:01:22,940
♪Til the day my kingdom is reclaimed♪

14
00:01:38,260 --> 00:01:42,540
=Her Blaze=

15
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:45,980
=Episode 13=

16
00:01:50,980 --> 00:01:51,980
The show is over.

17
00:01:52,090 --> 00:01:53,510
I'll give it back to you, Mr. Jiang.

18
00:01:54,570 --> 00:01:55,380
Here.

19
00:01:56,380 --> 00:01:58,580
You probably didn't get enough to eat
at the banquet.

20
00:02:01,980 --> 00:02:04,820
What happened on stage today
was a very important lesson to me.

21
00:02:05,930 --> 00:02:06,930
No one

22
00:02:06,930 --> 00:02:07,850
matters to me.

23
00:02:09,690 --> 00:02:12,570
If I want to climb higher,
I have to rely on myself.

24
00:02:18,730 --> 00:02:19,540
Well said.

25
00:02:24,980 --> 00:02:25,850
That's the Rao Yuci

26
00:02:25,850 --> 00:02:27,340
I've been hoping to see.

27
00:02:33,820 --> 00:02:36,890
Chen Xi is currently suspended
and under investigation for some reason.

28
00:02:38,860 --> 00:02:41,560
The head position in Investment Dept 2
is vacant for the time being.

29
00:02:42,290 --> 00:02:43,450
You should get ready

30
00:02:43,850 --> 00:02:45,610
to take over both Dept 2 and Dept 3.

31
00:02:48,780 --> 00:02:49,690
I'm just wondering

32
00:02:50,380 --> 00:02:53,130
what Bai Liangliang and Bai Muran

33
00:02:53,890 --> 00:02:54,690
will do next.

34
00:02:56,380 --> 00:02:57,170
Don't worry.

35
00:02:58,540 --> 00:02:59,570
Halfway up the mountain,

36
00:02:59,580 --> 00:03:00,980
we don't just rely on our own legs.

37
00:03:02,270 --> 00:03:04,390
We also need to make good use
of the forces around us.

38
00:03:04,900 --> 00:03:06,130
That's how you climb steadily.

39
00:03:07,040 --> 00:03:08,380
I've always been curious.

40
00:03:09,980 --> 00:03:11,400
What's your relationship

41
00:03:12,220 --> 00:03:13,610
with Bai Liangliang?

42
00:03:17,060 --> 00:03:17,850
Friends.

43
00:03:18,660 --> 00:03:19,890
Very good friends.

44
00:03:21,700 --> 00:03:25,100
(Five years earlier)

45
00:03:25,100 --> 00:03:26,100
I'm not like you.

46
00:03:26,500 --> 00:03:27,940
I could never be a genius.

47
00:03:28,130 --> 00:03:29,730
But I've always been curious.

48
00:03:29,850 --> 00:03:31,610
What goes on inside

49
00:03:31,610 --> 00:03:33,260
that genius brain of yours every day?

50
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:41,500
Recently, I've only been thinking
about two things.

51
00:03:41,610 --> 00:03:42,340
First,

52
00:03:42,340 --> 00:03:43,890
we both have to get into

53
00:03:43,890 --> 00:03:45,220
Professor Han's graduate program.

54
00:03:46,260 --> 00:03:47,260
Second...

55
00:03:51,730 --> 00:03:54,340
I think I might want to give it a try
with Bai Muran.

56
00:03:56,690 --> 00:03:57,500
Really?

57
00:03:59,520 --> 00:04:00,990
I wish you two nothing but happiness.

58
00:04:01,660 --> 00:04:02,690
Thank you, Liangliang.

59
00:04:04,170 --> 00:04:05,130
(This "good friend")

60
00:04:06,010 --> 00:04:07,540
(taught me something.)

61
00:04:08,450 --> 00:04:09,170
(Everything)

62
00:04:09,170 --> 00:04:10,980
(can have side A and side B.)

63
00:04:11,170 --> 00:04:13,060
(Thesis Defense)
This is what it's supposed to be.

64
00:04:13,060 --> 00:04:14,140
(Title: Trading Strategies in
Financial Markets and Their Evaluation)

65
00:04:14,140 --> 00:04:15,390
(Candidate: Rao Yuci,
Advisor: Han Dehai)

66
00:04:15,410 --> 00:04:16,220
(The A-side)

67
00:04:17,140 --> 00:04:19,140
(was the wonderful friendship
I once believed)

68
00:04:19,410 --> 00:04:20,730
(and the pure love.)

69
00:04:22,540 --> 00:04:23,170
(Mr. Bai,)

70
00:04:23,170 --> 00:04:25,550
(what do you think about
the proposal I just came up with?)

71
00:04:26,930 --> 00:04:27,730
(The B-side)

72
00:04:29,020 --> 00:04:30,810
(was all the details
I used to overlook.)

73
00:04:31,900 --> 00:04:33,340
(A lingering glance,)

74
00:04:34,810 --> 00:04:36,410
(and a casual move.)

75
00:04:38,220 --> 00:04:39,020
Yes.

76
00:04:39,020 --> 00:04:40,020
You two stand together.

77
00:04:40,020 --> 00:04:40,810
Let's toast to ourselves.

78
00:04:40,810 --> 00:04:42,850
(Or maybe a few whispered words.)

79
00:04:42,850 --> 00:04:44,340
I don't like nerds.

80
00:04:44,730 --> 00:04:46,250
None of your ex-girlfriends

81
00:04:46,250 --> 00:04:47,700
was a genius.

82
00:04:48,300 --> 00:04:49,490
Doesn't that make you curious?

83
00:04:50,460 --> 00:04:51,250
(And)

84
00:04:52,370 --> 00:04:54,460
(those corners
where the sunlight never reached.)

85
00:05:17,580 --> 00:05:18,490
(But now,)

86
00:05:19,810 --> 00:05:22,220
(I finally have the ability
to see the whole picture.)

87
00:06:05,810 --> 00:06:07,170
Liangliang, look here.

88
00:06:07,590 --> 00:06:08,690
Smile.

89
00:06:14,100 --> 00:06:14,900
Come.

90
00:06:16,340 --> 00:06:17,980
Look happy. Look over there.

91
00:06:26,860 --> 00:06:29,620
(Are your diplomat parents doing well?
Rao Yuci)

92
00:06:40,730 --> 00:06:41,370
Rao Yuci,

93
00:06:41,370 --> 00:06:42,810
what exactly are you plotting?

94
00:06:43,170 --> 00:06:44,220
What are you trying to do?

95
00:06:49,140 --> 00:06:50,250
Do you want to know

96
00:06:50,250 --> 00:06:51,410
the secret behind that photo?

97
00:06:52,410 --> 00:06:54,410
Where is the father
you've been searching for?

98
00:06:55,730 --> 00:06:57,140
Let's make a deal.

99
00:06:58,250 --> 00:06:59,050
Fine.

100
00:06:59,730 --> 00:07:00,540
Good.

101
00:07:00,850 --> 00:07:02,050
At tomorrow's regular meeting,

102
00:07:03,370 --> 00:07:05,140
between you, me, and Bai Muran,

103
00:07:05,610 --> 00:07:07,220
make a choice I'm happy with.

104
00:07:46,490 --> 00:07:47,290
Liangliang!

105
00:07:56,170 --> 00:07:56,980
Liang.

106
00:07:57,340 --> 00:07:58,660
Look, it's done.

107
00:08:07,660 --> 00:08:09,290
Liang, look at this.

108
00:08:09,980 --> 00:08:11,100
I bought you a new dress.

109
00:08:11,100 --> 00:08:11,930
Do you like it?

110
00:08:12,050 --> 00:08:12,900
Look. Do you like it?

111
00:08:12,900 --> 00:08:14,220
I don't want this! I want my dad!

112
00:08:14,220 --> 00:08:14,850
Liang!

113
00:08:14,850 --> 00:08:16,540
I want my dad!

114
00:08:17,050 --> 00:08:19,020
I want my dad!

115
00:08:21,140 --> 00:08:21,930
Look.

116
00:08:22,410 --> 00:08:23,220
I...

117
00:08:23,340 --> 00:08:24,340
I bought you a lollipop.

118
00:08:24,340 --> 00:08:25,140
I don't want it!

119
00:08:25,140 --> 00:08:26,340
I want my dad!

120
00:08:26,580 --> 00:08:27,660
I don't want it!

121
00:08:28,980 --> 00:08:30,540
I want my dad.

122
00:08:31,100 --> 00:08:32,460
Bai Liangliang, listen to me!

123
00:08:33,460 --> 00:08:34,580
I'm your mom.

124
00:08:34,700 --> 00:08:35,890
There's no Dad here.

125
00:08:35,890 --> 00:08:36,700
Not now.

126
00:08:36,700 --> 00:08:38,180
Not never!

127
00:08:42,850 --> 00:08:43,650
I'm sorry.

128
00:08:44,300 --> 00:08:45,370
I promise you.

129
00:08:46,490 --> 00:08:47,180
I won't

130
00:08:47,180 --> 00:08:49,250
snap at you again.

131
00:08:53,580 --> 00:08:54,370
Liang.

132
00:09:01,490 --> 00:09:02,100
You did wrong.

133
00:09:02,100 --> 00:09:03,060
No dinner tonight.

134
00:09:03,060 --> 00:09:03,770
Go.

135
00:09:07,650 --> 00:09:08,490
You're getting

136
00:09:08,490 --> 00:09:09,940
more and more difficult to deal with.

137
00:09:10,060 --> 00:09:10,850
Take this.

138
00:09:10,860 --> 00:09:12,500
Go out and buy yourself
something to eat.

139
00:09:15,460 --> 00:09:17,100
(Twelve years earlier)

140
00:09:17,100 --> 00:09:18,100
Alright. Here we are.

141
00:09:20,370 --> 00:09:21,300
Be careful.

142
00:09:27,180 --> 00:09:27,980
Liang...

143
00:09:32,350 --> 00:09:34,990
The guy at the dry-cleaning shop
ran away and left us deep in debt.

144
00:09:35,370 --> 00:09:36,850
It hasn't even been two years,

145
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:38,700
and now you want me
to move to Linwei Alley

146
00:09:38,700 --> 00:09:39,460
and stay with him?

147
00:09:40,100 --> 00:09:41,250
What if he runs off again?

148
00:09:42,060 --> 00:09:42,940
Where do we go then?

149
00:09:46,370 --> 00:09:48,610
(No matter how my life may change,)

150
00:09:49,530 --> 00:09:50,650
(in my heart,)

151
00:09:51,370 --> 00:09:52,390
(you are the only father)

152
00:09:52,820 --> 00:09:54,580
(I will ever acknowledge.)

153
00:09:55,650 --> 00:09:56,980
(The house)

154
00:09:56,980 --> 00:09:58,180
(we once lived in together)

155
00:09:58,820 --> 00:10:00,460
(is my only home.)

156
00:10:03,140 --> 00:10:06,580
(For Sale.
Quality Property. Serious offers only)

157
00:10:07,010 --> 00:10:07,820
All these years,

158
00:10:07,820 --> 00:10:09,990
I've been trying to find
the first owner of this house.

159
00:10:10,300 --> 00:10:12,370
But it's changed hands many times.

160
00:10:12,390 --> 00:10:13,870
I haven't managed to track them down.

161
00:10:15,890 --> 00:10:17,890
(No matter what it takes,)

162
00:10:18,730 --> 00:10:20,130
(I will find you.)

163
00:10:20,940 --> 00:10:21,730
(Dad.)

164
00:10:41,740 --> 00:10:44,660
(Three days earlier)

165
00:10:55,220 --> 00:10:56,940
Mr. Jiang had prepared this for you.

166
00:10:57,610 --> 00:10:59,300
He hopes you'll present a new image

167
00:10:59,730 --> 00:11:00,890
at the Boundary Forum.

168
00:11:06,220 --> 00:11:07,130
From now on,

169
00:11:08,100 --> 00:11:09,130
once you walk out of here,

170
00:11:09,130 --> 00:11:10,450
you don't just present yourself,

171
00:11:11,370 --> 00:11:12,700
you represent Lysen.

172
00:11:13,340 --> 00:11:13,980
This suit

173
00:11:13,980 --> 00:11:15,420
is only the beginning.

174
00:11:16,130 --> 00:11:16,940
Miss Gao

175
00:11:17,700 --> 00:11:19,370
will buy you many more.

176
00:11:21,130 --> 00:11:22,370
The way you dress

177
00:11:24,890 --> 00:11:26,100
reflects the person you are.

178
00:11:32,060 --> 00:11:33,580
Mr. Jiang has called everyone here

179
00:11:33,580 --> 00:11:34,730
for a short meeting.

180
00:11:35,200 --> 00:11:38,060
Chen Xi has run into some issues
and is currently under investigation.

181
00:11:38,460 --> 00:11:39,580
So Dept 2

182
00:11:39,580 --> 00:11:40,850
is missing a head at the moment.

183
00:11:41,730 --> 00:11:42,530
Mr. Jiang

184
00:11:42,980 --> 00:11:44,420
would like to hear your opinions.

185
00:11:48,980 --> 00:11:49,770
Mr. Jiang,

186
00:11:50,580 --> 00:11:52,010
I'd like to nominate myself.

187
00:11:55,100 --> 00:11:56,850
I've had a long rest,

188
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:59,370
and I've been feeling
in great shape lately.

189
00:12:02,250 --> 00:12:04,700
Plus, my overseas assignment

190
00:12:05,300 --> 00:12:06,890
was completed quite successfully.

191
00:12:09,100 --> 00:12:10,060
I have both the ability

192
00:12:10,420 --> 00:12:12,130
and the responsibility to lead Dept 2

193
00:12:12,320 --> 00:12:14,010
and help push
forward the acquisition plan

194
00:12:14,010 --> 00:12:15,290
for the green building materials company.

195
00:12:15,650 --> 00:12:16,460
Of course,

196
00:12:17,220 --> 00:12:19,530
that also depends on
whether everyone here supports me.

197
00:12:25,250 --> 00:12:26,060
Mr. Bai,

198
00:12:26,770 --> 00:12:27,980
your contributions to Lysen

199
00:12:27,980 --> 00:12:29,340
are undeniable.

200
00:12:29,610 --> 00:12:30,770
And I believe

201
00:12:31,100 --> 00:12:33,010
you certainly have the ability
to lead Dept 2.

202
00:12:33,650 --> 00:12:35,060
But everyone sitting here today

203
00:12:35,340 --> 00:12:37,010
is the backbone of Lysen.

204
00:12:37,020 --> 00:12:38,380
Each of you has your own strengths.

205
00:12:38,650 --> 00:12:40,220
So we need to think carefully.

206
00:12:43,340 --> 00:12:44,130
Ms. Bai.

207
00:12:46,300 --> 00:12:47,220
What do you think?

208
00:12:54,850 --> 00:12:55,700
Mr. Jiang,

209
00:12:56,300 --> 00:12:57,370
to keep things fair,

210
00:12:58,060 --> 00:12:59,890
everyone here

211
00:13:00,490 --> 00:13:01,580
should vote.

212
00:13:04,610 --> 00:13:05,420
That works.

213
00:13:06,610 --> 00:13:08,890
Since Ms. Bai suggested it.

214
00:13:08,890 --> 00:13:10,100
To keep things fair,

215
00:13:10,460 --> 00:13:12,420
we'll do

216
00:13:12,820 --> 00:13:13,940
an anonymous vote.

217
00:13:15,850 --> 00:13:16,850
You all vote first.

218
00:13:17,650 --> 00:13:20,060
If it ends in a tie,

219
00:13:20,460 --> 00:13:21,250
I'll cast my vote.

220
00:13:21,980 --> 00:13:22,770
Ms. Ren.

221
00:13:24,820 --> 00:13:25,610
Ms. Rao.

222
00:13:25,610 --> 00:13:26,340
Thank you.

223
00:13:26,340 --> 00:13:27,130
Mr. Bai.

224
00:13:27,890 --> 00:13:28,700
Ms. Bai.

225
00:13:43,530 --> 00:13:44,880
(At tomorrow's regular meeting,)

226
00:13:45,060 --> 00:13:46,820
(between you, me, and Bai Muran,)

227
00:13:47,300 --> 00:13:48,890
(make a choice I'm happy with.)

228
00:13:58,346 --> 00:13:59,130
Mr. Jiang,

229
00:13:59,180 --> 00:14:00,530
I'll start counting the votes now.

230
00:14:03,340 --> 00:14:04,660
(Rao)

231
00:14:04,980 --> 00:14:06,580
Rao Yuci, one vote.

232
00:14:07,850 --> 00:14:09,490
Rao Yuci, two votes.

233
00:14:13,010 --> 00:14:14,730
(Bai)
Bai Muran, one vote.

234
00:14:24,420 --> 00:14:26,100
Rao Yuci, three votes.

235
00:14:35,820 --> 00:14:36,610
Looks like

236
00:14:37,490 --> 00:14:38,940
my vote isn't necessary.

237
00:14:40,940 --> 00:14:42,300
The result is fair.

238
00:14:43,340 --> 00:14:46,060
Ms. Rao Yuci will take over as the head
of Investment Dept 2.

239
00:14:50,180 --> 00:14:50,980
By the way,

240
00:14:51,460 --> 00:14:53,700
inform the colleagues in Dept 3

241
00:14:53,770 --> 00:14:55,530
to move to Dept 2's office.

242
00:14:56,460 --> 00:14:57,610
Yu Peidong

243
00:14:57,820 --> 00:14:59,300
has been complaining about the office

244
00:14:59,610 --> 00:15:01,180
for a long time.

245
00:15:01,490 --> 00:15:02,610
This should make him happy.

246
00:15:04,580 --> 00:15:05,650
Thank you, Mr. Jiang.

247
00:15:26,770 --> 00:15:28,490
Weren't you supposed to be on my side?

248
00:15:28,490 --> 00:15:29,850
You think I didn't want to be?

249
00:15:30,220 --> 00:15:32,010
Didn't you see the situation just now?

250
00:15:32,060 --> 00:15:33,460
Mr. Jiang suddenly called us in.

251
00:15:33,460 --> 00:15:34,530
The outcome was already decided.

252
00:15:34,530 --> 00:15:36,220
That position was always meant
for Rao Yuci.

253
00:15:36,220 --> 00:15:37,010
Is that

254
00:15:37,010 --> 00:15:37,940
what you told me before?

255
00:15:38,650 --> 00:15:39,460
Muran,

256
00:15:39,820 --> 00:15:41,610
get your mind right about all of this.

257
00:15:41,850 --> 00:15:43,490
If we go against Mr. Jiang now,

258
00:15:43,490 --> 00:15:45,100
what good will come of it?

259
00:15:45,340 --> 00:15:46,010
All it will do

260
00:15:46,010 --> 00:15:48,250
is make our position in Lysen
worse and worse.

261
00:16:12,700 --> 00:16:14,130
I've done everything you asked me to do.

262
00:16:14,130 --> 00:16:15,220
Now it's your turn.

263
00:16:15,460 --> 00:16:17,370
Where did you get that photo from?

264
00:16:18,460 --> 00:16:19,420
That's not important.

265
00:16:19,980 --> 00:16:23,220
What matters is whether you want to find
the person in that photo.

266
00:16:24,130 --> 00:16:26,060
Are you messing with me, Rao Yuci?

267
00:16:29,060 --> 00:16:30,250
The person in the photo

268
00:16:30,250 --> 00:16:31,980
used to work in Beauty Pearl Society.

269
00:16:32,300 --> 00:16:34,820
So Ms. Bai, if you find someone
from Beauty Pearl Society,

270
00:16:35,340 --> 00:16:36,980
you will get the answer.

271
00:16:45,420 --> 00:16:46,220
Liangliang,

272
00:16:46,500 --> 00:16:47,740
(Green Building Material
Acquisition Plan)

273
00:16:47,770 --> 00:16:49,700
did you read
Han Congfei's public account post?

274
00:16:50,060 --> 00:16:51,220
That guy is something else.

275
00:16:51,230 --> 00:16:53,690
He actually managed to keep in touch
with someone from Beauty Pearl Society.

276
00:16:55,700 --> 00:16:57,420
Send me Han Congfei's number.

277
00:17:13,900 --> 00:17:14,860
I've met

278
00:17:14,860 --> 00:17:15,940
the person you arranged.

279
00:17:16,180 --> 00:17:17,940
Everything has been taken care of

280
00:17:17,940 --> 00:17:19,050
based on your plan.

281
00:17:19,620 --> 00:17:20,420
Very good.

282
00:17:21,460 --> 00:17:22,700
If Bai Liangliang asks you

283
00:17:22,700 --> 00:17:23,940
about Beauty Pearl Society,

284
00:17:24,010 --> 00:17:25,050
stall her for now.

285
00:17:25,800 --> 00:17:28,500
Wait until I find the right moment,
then set up a meeting with her.

286
00:17:29,900 --> 00:17:30,700
Alright.

287
00:17:33,000 --> 00:17:34,380
We've known each other for so long,

288
00:17:34,380 --> 00:17:35,290
and I've never properly

289
00:17:35,290 --> 00:17:36,330
thanked you.

290
00:17:36,520 --> 00:17:37,770
How about I treat you to a meal?

291
00:17:38,290 --> 00:17:39,090
No need.

292
00:17:40,050 --> 00:17:40,730
We're just

293
00:17:40,730 --> 00:17:42,250
using each other, aren't we?

294
00:17:47,180 --> 00:17:47,980
Well then.

295
00:17:48,730 --> 00:17:50,770
There's someone
who's been acting strange.

296
00:17:50,770 --> 00:17:52,050
I'll help you look into it.

297
00:17:52,420 --> 00:17:53,770
I mean, that male doctor

298
00:17:53,770 --> 00:17:54,900
who's always around you.

299
00:17:55,460 --> 00:17:56,900
I don't think he's a simple man.

300
00:18:01,660 --> 00:18:02,460
Han Congfei,

301
00:18:02,910 --> 00:18:04,730
the most important rule
in our collaboration

302
00:18:04,730 --> 00:18:07,090
is that you don't investigate
the people around me.

303
00:18:09,900 --> 00:18:11,530
Keep that in mind. Don't cross the line.

304
00:18:12,860 --> 00:18:14,290
As long as you keep doing what I say

305
00:18:14,980 --> 00:18:16,380
and follow my instructions,

306
00:18:16,940 --> 00:18:19,250
I'll provide you with more material
for your interviews.

307
00:18:20,900 --> 00:18:21,700
I'm off.

308
00:18:33,420 --> 00:18:36,260
(Three years earlier)

309
00:18:39,090 --> 00:18:41,730
The moment to witness a dream
has finally arrived.

310
00:18:42,980 --> 00:18:45,700
"Efficiency larger than one."

311
00:18:45,980 --> 00:18:46,770
Young man,

312
00:18:47,290 --> 00:18:48,570
