313
00:18:49,180 --> 00:18:49,980
What is this?

314
00:18:50,050 --> 00:18:50,860
What is it?

315
00:18:51,420 --> 00:18:53,180
A perpetual motion machine.

316
00:18:54,700 --> 00:18:56,380
Can you demonstrate it for me?

317
00:18:56,980 --> 00:18:57,770
Impossible.

318
00:18:57,780 --> 00:19:00,140
How could I just show
something this valuable like that?

319
00:19:00,810 --> 00:19:02,050
The timing isn't right yet.

320
00:19:02,460 --> 00:19:03,660
I need someone

321
00:19:03,660 --> 00:19:06,050
to hold a product launch.

322
00:19:06,250 --> 00:19:07,980
At the launch event,

323
00:19:08,010 --> 00:19:09,220
I'll reveal my treasure

324
00:19:09,220 --> 00:19:10,420
to the world.

325
00:19:10,420 --> 00:19:10,940
Mister,

326
00:19:10,940 --> 00:19:11,730
in this world,

327
00:19:11,730 --> 00:19:12,940
no scientist

328
00:19:12,940 --> 00:19:13,810
or physicist

329
00:19:13,810 --> 00:19:14,660
can build a machine

330
00:19:14,660 --> 00:19:15,900
where the output energy

331
00:19:15,900 --> 00:19:17,620
is greater than the input.

332
00:19:17,700 --> 00:19:18,530
In other words,

333
00:19:18,530 --> 00:19:20,010
using 1,000 grams of force

334
00:19:20,010 --> 00:19:21,770
to pull 1,200 grams

335
00:19:22,010 --> 00:19:23,460
is impossible.

336
00:19:23,600 --> 00:19:26,290
Listen, if you keep
fooling around with that, I'll smash it

337
00:19:26,290 --> 00:19:27,140
and throw it out.

338
00:19:27,140 --> 00:19:28,660
I show it to the neighbors

339
00:19:28,660 --> 00:19:30,330
in the park every day.

340
00:19:30,490 --> 00:19:32,250
They all say I'm going to succeed.

341
00:19:39,060 --> 00:19:41,780
(Ambulance)

342
00:19:49,470 --> 00:19:50,570
The injury's pretty serious.

343
00:19:50,570 --> 00:19:51,530
Yeah. How did that happen?

344
00:19:51,530 --> 00:19:52,140
Oh no.

345
00:19:52,140 --> 00:19:53,050
She's coming out.

346
00:19:53,220 --> 00:19:54,700
There. There she is.

347
00:19:54,700 --> 00:19:55,330
She did it.

348
00:19:55,330 --> 00:19:57,570
That girl stabbed her own mother.

349
00:19:58,570 --> 00:20:00,700
You can't push kids too hard.

350
00:20:02,140 --> 00:20:03,010
Push them too far...

351
00:20:03,660 --> 00:20:04,330
Get in.

352
00:20:04,330 --> 00:20:04,980
Yes.

353
00:20:27,220 --> 00:20:28,900
Everyone, calm down.

354
00:20:28,940 --> 00:20:30,050
Calm down.

355
00:20:30,050 --> 00:20:31,090
Who made the call just now?

356
00:20:31,090 --> 00:20:32,250
Me. I did.

357
00:20:32,250 --> 00:20:33,010
This girl

358
00:20:33,010 --> 00:20:34,530
suddenly went crazy this morning

359
00:20:34,530 --> 00:20:35,810
and stabbed her mother.

360
00:20:35,810 --> 00:20:36,570
She completely lost control.

361
00:20:36,570 --> 00:20:36,770
Well,

362
00:20:36,770 --> 00:20:38,010
