363
00:20:38,010 --> 00:20:39,140
Well, this girl

364
00:20:39,140 --> 00:20:40,660
had a boyfriend,

365
00:20:40,660 --> 00:20:42,330
then they broke up.

366
00:20:42,330 --> 00:20:43,140
She has been a genius

367
00:20:43,140 --> 00:20:44,490
since she was little.

368
00:20:44,490 --> 00:20:46,250
Her grades were always excellent.

369
00:20:46,250 --> 00:20:46,940
But her mom

370
00:20:46,940 --> 00:20:48,290
kept pressuring her,

371
00:20:48,290 --> 00:20:50,460
and she couldn't take it anymore.

372
00:20:50,810 --> 00:20:51,620
Boss,

373
00:20:51,810 --> 00:20:53,090
didn't you promise

374
00:20:53,090 --> 00:20:54,900
