379
00:21:01,180 --> 00:21:02,090
Okay. No problem.

380
00:21:02,530 --> 00:21:03,330
Deal.

381
00:21:03,330 --> 00:21:04,770
- As soon as possible.
- Alright.

382
00:21:09,420 --> 00:21:13,380
