385
00:21:19,770 --> 00:21:20,570
Hello.

386
00:21:21,180 --> 00:21:21,980
Hello.

387
00:21:26,980 --> 00:21:28,530
Were you the one

388
00:21:28,530 --> 00:21:29,700
