a million-follower finance blogger.

408
00:22:17,420 --> 00:22:18,220
And that,

409
00:22:19,660 --> 00:22:20,730
I can help you.

410
00:22:35,860 --> 00:22:37,660
I almost believed you.

411
00:22:38,380 --> 00:22:39,980
If we weren't meeting here.

412
00:22:41,180 --> 00:22:43,090
If there's nothing else, let's call it a day.

413
00:22:44,050 --> 00:22:45,980
Why don't you take a look at this, Mr. Han?

414
00:22:48,490 --> 00:22:49,380
Jiang Dongchao.

415
00:22:53,260 --> 00:22:57,060
(Jiang Dongchao.
Education, Work Experience)

416
00:23:02,730 --> 00:23:04,330
Stories that everyone know

417
00:23:04,570 --> 00:23:05,730
