426
00:23:37,900 --> 00:23:39,390
How did you get all this information?

427
00:23:40,090 --> 00:23:41,570
You'll find out someday.

428
00:23:43,140 --> 00:23:44,660
But the next time we meet,

429
00:23:46,490 --> 00:23:47,900
