452
00:24:47,180 --> 00:24:47,900
What interests me

453
00:24:47,900 --> 00:24:49,090
is your story, Mr. Jiang.

454
00:24:49,420 --> 00:24:50,330
I believe

455
00:24:50,330 --> 00:24:53,010
