482
00:26:21,380 --> 00:26:22,140
I think

483
00:26:22,140 --> 00:26:23,900
you know better than everyone

484
00:26:25,050 --> 00:26:26,090
that to me,

485
00:26:27,220 --> 00:26:28,940
Mr. Yu will always be Manager Yu.

486
00:26:29,530 --> 00:26:30,660
And I believe

487
00:26:31,380 --> 00:26:32,770
