492
00:26:46,940 --> 00:26:47,730
Sure.

493
00:26:48,460 --> 00:26:50,940
I'll wait for you, Mr. Han.

494
00:27:18,900 --> 00:27:20,090
The person in the photo

495
00:27:20,090 --> 00:27:21,900
