502
00:27:45,660 --> 00:27:46,530
Company notice.

503
00:27:46,730 --> 00:27:47,700
Starting today,

504
00:27:47,940 --> 00:27:51,050
Rao Yuci, head of Dept 3,
will also oversee Dept 2.

505
00:27:51,380 --> 00:27:52,220
From today on,

506
00:27:52,220 --> 00:27:53,290
Dept 2 and Dept 3

507
00:27:53,620 --> 00:27:54,700
