508
00:27:54,700 --> 00:27:56,380
We'll be working together?

509
00:27:56,380 --> 00:27:57,140
No idea.

510
00:28:15,220 --> 00:28:16,140
I'm sure most of you

511
00:28:16,140 --> 00:28:17,700
