539
00:29:33,860 --> 00:29:35,530
Just call me Yu from now on.

540
00:29:35,940 --> 00:29:37,180
Please look out for us.

541
00:29:38,860 --> 00:29:39,900
I'll sit over there.

542
00:29:51,660 --> 00:29:52,900
Look at him.

543
00:29:53,420 --> 00:29:54,220
Seriously.

544
00:29:54,420 --> 00:29:55,530
Look at that fellow.

545
00:29:56,010 --> 00:29:57,700
Those from Dept 3 are like that.

546
00:29:59,460 --> 00:30:02,540
(Rao Yuci: Mr. Yu, let's talk.)

547
00:30:02,540 --> 00:30:05,180
(Yu Peidong: There's nothing
to talk about.)

548
00:30:05,380 --> 00:30:09,500
(Investment Dept 3: You have been
removed from the group chat.)

549
00:30:47,620 --> 00:30:48,420
Sir.

550
00:30:50,570 --> 00:30:51,250
Give me

551
00:30:51,250 --> 00:30:52,570
