553
00:30:53,570 --> 00:30:55,330
Gang, one copper hotpot here.

554
00:30:55,900 --> 00:30:56,700
Sir.

555
00:30:58,330 --> 00:31:00,090
Put my bill on her tab.

556
00:31:01,660 --> 00:31:02,460
Alright.

557
00:31:02,810 --> 00:31:05,090
