568
00:31:35,077 --> 00:31:36,250
I'd suggest

569
00:31:36,460 --> 00:31:38,010
you listen to Ms. Ren in the future.

570
00:31:42,980 --> 00:31:44,050
What do you mean by that?

571
00:31:44,730 --> 00:31:45,730
Nothing much.

572
00:31:47,250 --> 00:31:48,900
I'll find a chance
to thank her properly.

573
00:31:53,090 --> 00:31:53,900
Rao Yuci.

574
00:31:56,570 --> 00:31:58,290
Aren't you worried

575
00:31:59,300 --> 00:32:00,420
I might take this seriously?

576
00:32:01,460 --> 00:32:02,900
If you do, that's fine.

577
00:32:04,180 --> 00:32:05,810
I won't be staying for very long anyway.

578
00:32:06,290 --> 00:32:07,090
Soon enough,

579
00:32:07,980 --> 00:32:08,730
every position

580
00:32:08,730 --> 00:32:09,860
will go back to its owner.

581
00:32:11,460 --> 00:32:12,940
I can't have friends at Lysen.

582
00:32:13,940 --> 00:32:14,730
So

583
00:32:15,810 --> 00:32:16,980
in front of others,

584
00:32:17,860 --> 00:32:18,940
keep your distance from me.

585
00:32:19,660 --> 00:32:20,620
But in private,

586
00:32:21,620 --> 00:32:22,700
we're still friends.

587
00:32:30,530 --> 00:32:31,460
Alright then, friend.

588
00:32:33,110 --> 00:32:34,490
In that case, I'll move over here.

589
00:33:00,940 --> 00:33:02,010
Back to business.

590
00:33:04,860 --> 00:33:06,570
Lysen has started

591
00:33:06,940 --> 00:33:09,700
buying up those green building
materials companies.

592
00:33:11,010 --> 00:33:12,900
But Bosi has been unusually quiet.

593
00:33:12,900 --> 00:33:14,250
Don't you find that strange?

594
00:33:16,330 --> 00:33:17,700
Everyone does.

595
00:33:19,330 --> 00:33:20,380
But everyone

596
00:33:21,860 --> 00:33:23,810
seems to be waiting

597
00:33:23,810 --> 00:33:24,980
for Mr. Jiang to ask it,

598
00:33:25,940 --> 00:33:27,050
so someone else can answer.

599
00:33:29,050 --> 00:33:30,420
But they're also afraid

600
00:33:30,420 --> 00:33:31,890
the question they ask

601
00:33:32,980 --> 00:33:34,010
might backfire on them.

602
00:33:34,860 --> 00:33:36,510
So they keep those questions

603
00:33:37,380 --> 00:33:39,010
off the table
and deal with them quietly.

604
00:33:41,140 --> 00:33:43,660
And you?

605
00:33:44,420 --> 00:33:45,330
Do you have an answer?

606
00:33:47,300 --> 00:33:48,330
No matter how messy the situation is,

607
00:33:48,330 --> 00:33:50,580
there's always a logic
that leads to the final outcome.

608
00:33:51,260 --> 00:33:53,860
It's just that once those questions
are brought out into the open,

609
00:33:55,010 --> 00:33:55,770
Mr. Jiang

610
00:33:55,770 --> 00:33:56,980
might not like it.

611
00:33:58,810 --> 00:34:00,700
What do you think, Mr. Yu?

612
00:34:08,220 --> 00:34:11,888
=Episode 13=
(Your Home Turf)

613
00:34:12,380 --> 00:34:14,820
(All animals in this production
were treated humanely)

614
00:34:14,820 --> 00:34:21,020
♪Take a breath and swallow
the words you couldn't say♪

615
00:34:21,780 --> 00:34:24,980
♪No need to force your heart anymore♪

616
00:34:24,980 --> 00:34:29,500
♪Searching for the season
we once missed♪

617
00:34:29,500 --> 00:34:37,020
♪Leave this place,
though wounded still stay strong♪

618
00:34:37,020 --> 00:34:40,940
♪You must believe
one day the rain will fall♪

619
00:34:40,940 --> 00:34:44,980
♪And wash away the mud
that stains your soul♪

620
00:34:44,980 --> 00:34:48,500
♪Find your freedom in the wild♪

621
00:34:48,500 --> 00:34:52,460
♪Take your stride and move ahead♪

622
00:34:52,460 --> 00:34:56,620
♪I will stay behind
and wait for your eyes♪

623
00:34:56,620 --> 00:35:00,820
♪To rebuild
the same flesh and soul again♪

624
00:35:00,820 --> 00:35:04,620
♪Wander freely through the thorns♪

625
00:35:04,620 --> 00:35:08,700
♪Keep walking through the light♪

626
00:35:08,700 --> 00:35:12,900
♪Fate is absurd, don't stop for anyone♪

627
00:35:12,900 --> 00:35:19,220
♪What you dare to lose
will one day be your own♪

628
00:35:36,340 --> 00:35:42,980
♪I'm sorry, I still owe you these words♪

629
00:35:42,980 --> 00:35:46,820
♪An apology that came too late♪

630
00:35:46,820 --> 00:35:51,460
♪Yet it's also the path
that saves my soul♪

631
00:35:51,540 --> 00:35:58,940
♪When the cold wind
passes it takes the past away♪

632
00:35:58,940 --> 00:36:03,020
♪You must believe and stand unwavering♪

633
00:36:03,020 --> 00:36:07,100
♪There will be hands
to pull you from the deep♪

634
00:36:07,100 --> 00:36:11,100
♪Find your freedom in the silence♪

635
00:36:11,100 --> 00:36:14,860
♪Let your wounds be mended♪

636
00:36:14,860 --> 00:36:19,060
♪Gray is not the past
and pain is not a shame♪

637
00:36:19,060 --> 00:36:23,220
♪Sometimes the sunlight
makes the world look crueler♪

638
00:36:23,220 --> 00:36:26,940
♪Wander through the echoes of regret♪

639
00:36:26,940 --> 00:36:30,980
♪Be forgiven and be sheltered♪

640
00:36:30,980 --> 00:36:35,020
♪After everything shatters,
hold my hand♪

641
00:36:35,020 --> 00:36:41,220
♪A flower reborn
will finally bloom forever♪
